cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation and normalization. The use of adversarial training also suggests that it may belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of multiple datasets and the evaluation of results suggest that it may also belong to the neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
